accessibility.text: Attractive and stylish visualizations are made by filming various trendy items that can be found within the shops of the MGM from an extremely close angle with a hi-def camera. This produces unusual and difficult to recognize images. The video content changes periodically (every week) intriguing visitors and encouraging them to participate in a guessing game: The first user to correctly guess what item is displayed in a particular video can win that item (or some other prize).
This scenario (or similar) can be integrated into MGM's marketing strategy and act as advertising for the shops that provide the prize item in order to participate in the Micro Footage Game.
Visuals are only mood references,  original content will be designed.
